{"word":"G4508 - ῥυπαρός - rhyparós - rhoo-par-os' - Vile","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥυπαρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">rhyparós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">rhoo-par-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Vile</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கந்தையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"filthy, dirty: properly, of clothing vile"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4509 - ῥύπος - rhýpos - hroo'-pos/4509\">G4509</a>; <i>dirty</i>, that is, (relatively) <i>cheap</i> or <i>shabby</i>; morally <i>wicked:</i> - vile.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}